posts.post_title: Large Number of T206's For Sale
posts.post_content:
I'm currently looking to sell a large chunk of my T206 collection.  I'm looking to sell about 50 cards all graded, and if I can't sell them on here will post them as BIN on eBay but would rather avoid the fee's.  Prices are negotiable, but if you're willing to meet the asking price it's a done deal.  Email with questions or offers [url]wilsonic89@yahoo.com[/url].  Scans of all cards are available on request.
